<![CDATA[<div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Hi&nbsp;{!Account.Client_First_Name__c},</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">We’re excited to be able to offer you the opportunity to import your contacts to the Yodle dashboard directly from your Apple device. &nbsp;In order to have those contacts sync, you will need to update your iCloud settings on your phone, tablet, or desktop. &nbsp;I’ve included the instructions below to help you get this set up. &nbsp;Once you’ve completed the steps below, please log back in to the Yodle dashboard and attempt the Import from Apple process again.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">If you have any questions at all, please contact us. &nbsp;Thanks so much and have a great day!</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">How to set up iCloud sync for Contacts:</font></div><div><ol><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Open the Settings app on your device.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Click the iCloud option.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">You may be prompted to enter your iCloud email and password. &nbsp;If you are, enter and tap next.<br><i>*If you haven’t set up your iCloud account yet, you will need to complete that process from this page first.</i></font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Once completed, click the switch next to Contacts to turn on the sync.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Allow 5-10 minutes to sync and then attempt the import process through the Yodle dashboard.</font></li></ol></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Sincerely,</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><i style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 0);"><br></i></font></div><div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>{!User.Full_Name__c}</b></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>&nbsp;</b></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Yodle Customer Care</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">(877) 334-4321</font></div></div>]]></td>
